cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this repository, please cite the software release."
title: "TCGA/GDC tumor-vs-normal RNA-seq classifier"
version: "v2.0.0-gdc-starcounts"
date-released: "2026-07-12"
type: software
license: MIT
authors:
  - given-names: Koju
    family-names: Maruyama
repository-code: "https://github.com/maruyamakoju/tcga-classifier-deliverables"
abstract: >-
  Lightweight deployment release for a TCGA/GDC STAR-Counts-scale bulk RNA-seq
  tumor-vs-adjacent-normal classifier, with input QC, scoring, threshold
  calibration, explanations, release validation, reproducible training and
  validation entry points, and compact external-validation artifacts. The
  public scoring library API is version 3.0.0.
keywords:
  - TCGA
  - GDC
  - RNA-seq
  - tumor-normal classification
  - bioinformatics
  - machine learning
